summary: Marie Claire had a couple of v.short interviews w/Jodie Comer (loving her in Killing Eve) + Hannah Weiland of Shrimps. Next...
body:
Marie Claire had a couple of v.short interviews w/Jodie Comer (loving her in Killing Eve) + Hannah Weiland of Shrimps. Next month their free gift is a full size Rituals hand balm.

Saw last episode of Wanderlust. I thought it was OK but sort of less than the sum of its parts, if that makes sense. It had a fantastic cast but it didn’t really appeal to me as much as I thought I would. And I’m sorry but I wish the Toni Collette character had ended up w/Paul Kaye’s character (mainly because I’ve always had a bit of a thing for him even going right back to when he was doing Dennis Pennis). Thought Zawe Ashton was really good in it as well.
